						               													<description>Cthulhu: XOTHIC WARS is the master rules set for a new 28mm Monster Skirmish Game. It is based around the Aliens of the HP Lovecraft mythos, and will cover all main 7 species.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The premise is the wars fought on Earth before the rise of mankind. Each core box in the wave will be complimented by a separate campaign book. It is flexible enough to include use for play in eras with man where the Aliens were also present.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The miniatures will start with the Starspawn of Cthulhu, as they engage the Elder Things for domination of the newly formed planet. We want these miniatures for ourselves, so will be sculpting and printing all of the races regardless. So the Mi-Go and the rest are in the pipeline.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Miniatures will include resin masters for collectors, and are done in 28mm for most popular ranges. Additionally they scale nicely for 15mm and 6mm gamers.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
